PNI version 0.01
================

PNI stands for Perl Node Interface.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

File::Find
Test::More
Time::HiRes

